# MGA operator pipeline tooling — track the PORTABLE, reusable pipeline + its
# structured inputs; keep machine-local scratch, run output, and secrets local.
#
# This is a PUBLIC repo. The hard gate (see rules/non-code-public-repo-guardrails):
# NOTHING with a literal operator-absolute path (a `C:\Users\<name>\...` /
# `/Users/<name>/...` home dir) or a claude session-UUID scratch path may be
# committed.
# The durable pipeline scripts are path-clean (they derive dirs from
# `Path.home()` / `os.environ["TEMP"]`), so they ARE tracked. Ad-hoc diagnostics
# that hardcode this machine's paths stay local (protected from a stray
# `git clean` by hooks/block-git-clean.js) until scrubbed to portable idioms.
#
# Tracked (necessary to RE-RUN the pipeline — the scripts read these):
#   - portable .py / .ps1 pipeline tooling (no hardcoded operator path)
#   - *-lineup-expert.md            — path-clean domain knowledge
#   - <agent>-spans/<map>.json      — structured ingest source-of-truth
#   - *_items.json                  — per-chapter work lists (localization input)
#   - *_accept.json                 — externalized accept mappings (gating input)
#   - .env.r2.example
#
# Ignored (run output / human notes / machine-local / secret):
#   - LOCALIZE_INSTRUCTIONS*.md, dump_*, and the diagnostics listed below
#     (hardcode operator-absolute paths — machine-local operator briefs/scratch)
#   - *.block, *_results.json       raw localizer output (embed local card paths)
#   - *_spans.md, *-ledger.md, *-spans notes  human notes (paths + reasoning)
#   - strips / frames / logs / __pycache__ / the .env.r2 credential file

# --- Secrets (NEVER track) ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.r2.example

# --- Machine-local operator briefs + ad-hoc diagnostics (hardcode this
#     machine's absolute paths — keep local until scrubbed to Path.home() idioms) ---
LOCALIZE_INSTRUCTIONS*.md
dump_*.py
dump_*.ps1
backfill_market_door.py
diagnose_aim_localizer.py
finecut_strip.py
landing_pad_compare_sheet.py
market_door_strip.py
parse_and_recut.py
recut_from_output.py
recut_landing_pad_check.py
relocalize_aim.py
rerun_market_door_micro.py
scan_multidemo.py

# --- Raw localizer run OUTPUT (embed machine-local card paths) ---
*.block
*_results.json

# --- Human working-notes / ledgers (local paths + internal gating reasoning) ---
# Top-level notes + everything non-.json inside a *-spans/ dir (per-lineup
# notes, addenda, txt). Only the structured <map>.json in a spans dir is input.
*_spans.md
*-ledger.md
*-spans/*.md
*-spans/**/*.md
*-spans/*.txt
*-spans/**/*.txt

# --- Extracted media / frame strips (regenerable from the source video) ---
_strips/
*_strips/
frames/
_scratch/

# --- Logs ---
*.log
_*.log

# --- Python bytecode cache ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# --- Pin-proposer run artifacts (embed machine-local frame paths) ---
*-pin-requests.json
*-pin-proposals.json
